[2026-04-14 13:58:14 Europe/London] [DEBUG]   DEBUG: Property SQL Params: ["34518933","Orme Villa, Trefor",5,"34518933-orme-villa-trefor","Orme Villa",193,107,31747,"LL54 5LB","Tudors are pleased to present this well-maintained detached bungalow located in the charming seaside village of Trefor, enjoying attractive mountain views and within walking distance of the beach and local village amenities.The accommodation is in good decorative order throughout and includes a welc","Tudors are pleased to present this well-maintained detached bungalow located in the charming seaside village of Trefor, enjoying attractive mountain views and within walking distance of the beach and local village amenities.<br\/><br\/>The accommodation is in good decorative order throughout and includes a welcoming lounge featuring a fireplace, as well as a separate sitting room with a multifuel stove, creating warm and characterful living spaces. There are two bedrooms on the ground floor, along with a useful loft room accessed via a steep staircase, offering additional versatile space. The accommodation briefly comprises of the following:- Entrance Porch. Hallway. Lounge. Two Bedrooms. Shower Room. Sitting Room. Kitchen. Rear Porch. Loft Room.<br\/><br\/>The property has recently benefited from significant energy efficiency improvements through the ECO4 scheme, including the installation of an air source heat pump, battery pack, and upgraded wall insulation. <br\/><br\/>This bungalow offers a lovely opportunity for those seeking a home in a peaceful village setting. Viewing highly recommended.",280000,"",56,2,1,0,"52.996166","-4.420391","34518933",1,1,0,1,1,"2026-04-12","2026-04-12",0,5,0,0,0,"https:\/\/alto-live.s3.amazonaws.com\/76JgrfysZIql31f8M1ILXgo-sMM\/AtzYqd4FZlsWUrAiaBc6jsn-YsA\/Brochure\/[0]\/sXbHKfGHX0OI6cgrzU1EiQ.pdf","","","","","","","","",""]
