[2026-04-14 14:02:06 Europe/London] [DEBUG]   DEBUG: Property SQL Params: ["32009486","Clynnogfawr, Caernarfon",6,"32009486-clynnogfawr-caernarfon","Tal Eryr",193,107,31769,"LL54 5PS","4.16 ACRES*FIVE BEDROOMS*ACCESS TO BEACH*VIEWING RECOMMENDEDTudor Estate Agents & Chartered Surveyors are favoured with instructions to offer for sale this secluded detached residence, set in approximately 4.16 acres (plan available on request), enjoying spectacular panoramic sea and mountain views.","4.16 ACRES*FIVE BEDROOMS*ACCESS TO BEACH*VIEWING RECOMMENDED<br\/>Tudor Estate Agents & Chartered Surveyors are favoured with instructions to offer for sale this secluded detached residence, set in approximately 4.16 acres (plan available on request), enjoying spectacular panoramic sea and mountain views.<br\/>The property is located in an elevated rural position on the north coast of the glorious Llyn Peninsula, within convenient reach of Caernarfon and Pwllheli.<br\/>The spacious accommodation benefits from double glazing and oil-fired central heating and briefly comprises: Ground Floor: Porch. Hall. Two Bedrooms. Kitchen\/Diner. Bathroom. Utility Room. First Floor: Three Bedrooms. Shower Room. Lounge \u2013 all enjoying the stunning coastal views. The property is approached via a right of way over the adjoining property. A separate private driveway from the main road to Tal Eryr exists but is not currently in use. Gardens and grounds surround the residence, with two static caravans located on site. Please note that the caravans are not in a habitable condition.<br\/>A public footpath leads from the property down to the pebbled beach \u2013 a fantastic spot to enjoy sunsets. Viewing is highly recommended to appreciate the setting and potential of this unique coastal property.",475000,"",56,5,2,2,"53.004695","-4.392786","32009486",1,1,0,1,1,"2025-11-26","2025-11-26",0,5,0,0,0,"https:\/\/alto-live.s3.amazonaws.com\/76JgrfysZIql31f8M1ILXgo-sMM\/AtzYqd4FZlsWUrAiaBc6jsn-YsA\/Brochure\/[0]\/