tairs Toilet.  Four Bedrooms & Bathroom on the first floor. Drive & Ample Parking. Delightful Gardens & Grounds all benefitting from the spectacular views. Garage. <br\/>A viewing is highly recommended to truly appreciate the stunning location and views.",475000,"",56,4,1,3,"52.902923","-4.4019","33670190",1,1,0,1,1,"2026-04-08","2026-04-08",0,5,0,0,0,"https:\/\/alto-live.s3.amazonaws.com\/76JgrfysZIql31f8M1ILXgo-sMM\/AtzYqd4FZlsWUrAiaBc6jsn-YsA\/Brochure\/[0]\/cRHFW7tr70uZZ7Nh-vlYfg.pdf","","","","","","","","",""]
