[2026-04-14 14:03:23 Europe/London] [DEBUG]   DEBUG: Property SQL Params: ["34092446","Boduan, Pwllheli",6,"34092446-boduan-pwllheli","Coed Genau",193,107,31754,"LL53 6DT","Tudor Estate Agents & Chartered Surveyors are delighted to offer for sale this stunning rural detached residence, situated in an elevated position, in the heart of the glorious Llyn Peninsula and is convenient for Nefyn and Morfa Nefyn on the North coast and Pwllheli, the market town for the area on","Tudor Estate Agents & Chartered Surveyors are delighted to offer for sale this stunning rural detached residence, situated in an elevated position, in the heart of the glorious Llyn Peninsula and is convenient for Nefyn and Morfa Nefyn on the North coast and Pwllheli, the market town for the area on the South coast. A rare opportunity to acquire this beautifully presented detached home, which has undergone a comprehensive programme of renovation, extension, and enhancement, resulting in a stylish and comfortable living environment tailored to modern lifestyle. Every detail has been thoughtfully considered. <br\/>Set within a generous plot, the property now offers spacious, light-filled interiors with a seamless flow between living areas. The heart of the home is a stunning open-plan living\/dining\/kitchen with high-spec fittings, and patio doors opening onto the patio garden - perfect for entertaining or relaxing. The kitchen has the benefit of a walk-in pantry, utility room, boot room & downstairs toilet. At the opposite end of the property, a separate sitting room provides a peaceful retreat. On the first floor, the principal bedroom enjoys the luxury of a walk-in wardrobe and an en-suite. Two further Bedrooms and  Family Bathroom. <br\/>Externally, the property boasts ample driveway parking and an attractive landscaped garden,  thoughtfully designed with patio seating areas. A standout feature is the Luxury Pod, offering a fully self-contained living space complete with a stylish kitchen area, shower room, and its own private seating area - perfect for guests or a peaceful home office retreat.",790000,"",56,3,2,2,"52.909992","-4.494737","34092446",1,1,0,1,1,"2025-08-14","2025-08-14",0,5,0,0,0,"https:\/\/alto-live.s3.amazonaws.com\/76JgrfysZIql31f8M1ILXgo-sMM\/AtzYqd4FZlsWUrAiaBc6jsn-YsA\/Brochure\/[0]\/NE9LUO7VoEibrwxrAHHO9Q.pdf","","","","","","","","",""]
